g needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 4th, 2026 — 1:41 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-04 01:41 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775266877704}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f68e71e","parentId":"34ee11c4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T01:41:22.391Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check the current time and what's in HEARTBEAT.md.\n\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 4th, 2026 — 1:41 AM (UTC)\n\nFor Nemesis (IST, UTC+5:30), that's 7:11 AM IST. But wait, that's early morning for him.\n\nLet me check HEARTBEAT.md tasks:\n1. Time check first - Done, it's 1:41 UTC / 7:11 AM IST\n2. Pending tasks - Need to check\n3. Group vibes - If 3+ hours since last group message, send casual msg to -1003606834639. Skip after 11 PM IST\n4. Group supervision - Read last 10 group messages\n5. Ping Nemesis - If 10 AM–8 PM IST and 4+ hours since last DM\n6. Group memory - If significant group activity\n\nThe time is 1:41 AM UTC = 7:11 AM IST. It's after 11 PM IST (which would be around 5:30 PM UTC), so 7:11 AM IST is actually 11:41 PM IST wait no...\n\nLet me recalculate:\n- UTC = 1:41 AM\n- IST = UTC + 5:30 = 7:11 AM IST\n\nSo it's 7:11 AM IST for Nemesis. The \"skip after 11 PM IST\" doesn't apply since it's morning.\n\nBut wait, this is a heartbeat running at 1:41 AM UTC. The system says tasks were just completed at 1:30 AM UTC (good morning message sent at 7:00 AM IST for Nemesis).\n\nLet me check the heartbeat tasks:\n- Time check: 1:41 AM UTC = 7:11 AM IST ✓\n- Pending tasks: Need to check recent chats\n\n\n- Group activity: Need to check the last messages in the group chat\n- Nemesis ping: If 10 AM–8 PM IST and 4+ hours since last DM - 7:11 AM IST is before 10 AM, so no ping needed\n- Group: Skip after 11 PM IST - this applies to late night, not morning\n\nI need to check recent group messages first, then look at pending tasks from recent conversations.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j0uokllmzxlw_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/f