{"type":"message","id":"ea8ecc44","parentId":"c5710ddb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T01:41:45.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No active group sessions. Let me check the last messages that were sent to the group. Based on the system messages, good-morning (group) is at 8 AM IST, and the last good-night was at 10 PM IST.\n\nCurrent time: 1:41 AM UTC = 7:11 AM IST\n\nThe group tasks:\n- Group vibes: If 3+ hours since last group message, send casual msg. Skip after 11 PM IST.\n- 7:11 AM IST - the 8 AM good-morning cron would have run ~4 hours ago (at 2:30 AM UTC). But it's also before 10 AM so no Nemesis ping needed.\n\nWait, let me recalculate. The good-morning (group) runs at 8 AM IST. That's 2:30 AM UTC. So if it's 1:41 AM UTC, the 8 AM IST cron hasn't run yet today. The last group message would have been the goodnight-story at 10 PM IST = 4:30 PM UTC yesterday.\n\nSo from 4:30 PM UTC yesterday to 1:41 AM UTC today = about 9 hours. That's more than 3 hours. BUT the rule says \"skip after 11 PM IST\" - that's 5:30 PM UTC. Since it's 1:41 AM UTC (which is after 5:30 PM UTC), I should skip the group message.\n\nActually wait, let me re-read: \"Skip after 11 PM IST\" - this means don't send group messages late at night local time. But it's now 7:11 AM IST - that's morning, not night. The \"skip after 11 PM\" applies to late night hours, not morning.\n\nBut the more important point: if it's only 7:11 AM IST, that's BEFORE 10 AM, so no Nemesis ping anyway. And the group message rule says \"3+ hours since last group message\" - yes it's been more than 3 hours, but the skip after 11 PM is about late night, not morning.\n\nActually, I think I'm overthinking this. \n\nThe checklist is straightforward: time check is done, pending tasks don't seem to require action, and it's currently 7:11 AM IST which is before the 10 AM threshold so I don't need to ping Nemesis. Since there's no active group session to pull history from, I'll stick with HEARTBEAT_OK.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xibnlijokzlh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":107,"output":998,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775266899963,"responseId":"gen-1775266900-M8ElW033OXD2pakugMH7"}}
