{"type":"message","id":"8e33a3e0","parentId":"03563140","timestamp":"2026-04-04T01:41:51.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me calculate:\n- Current time: 1:41 AM UTC on April 4\n- Last group message: April 3 at 15:21 UTC = 8:51 PM IST\n- Hours since: 1:41 AM UTC - 15:21 UTC = ~10.2 hours = ~4.7 hours IST\n\nWait, that's backwards. Let me recalculate:\n- From 15:21 UTC on April 3 to 01:41 UTC on April 4\n- That's 10 hours 20 minutes\n- In IST: 10 hours 20 minutes since 8:51 PM IST = ~7:11 AM IST on April 4\n\nSo it's been about 10+ hours since the last group message, which is more than 3 hours. BUT it's 7:11 AM IST now and the rule says \"Skip after 11 PM IST\" - but that's for late night. This is morning, so not applicable.\n\nBUT wait - the current time is 1:41 AM UTC which is 7:11 AM IST. The \"skip after 11 PM IST\" applies to the sender - if I'm sending messages after 11 PM IST, I should skip. Since it's 7:11 AM IST, that's fine to send.\n\nLet me re-read the heartbeat tasks:\n- \"Group vibes: If 3+ hours since last group message, send casual msg to -1003606834639. Skip after 11 PM IST.\"\n\nSo: 3+ hours since last group message (✓ - it's been ~10 hours), and not after 11 PM IST (it's 7:11 AM IST, so fine).\n\nBut wait - the last group message was at 15:21 UTC = 8:51 PM IST on April 3. Now it's 7:11 AM IST on April 4. That's 10+ hours since last group message.\n\nSo I should send a casual group message!\n\nBut hold on - it's 1:41 AM UTC for me, which is late night. The \"Skip after 11 PM IST\" might be referring to MY local time or Nemesis's time. \n\nLooking at this more carefully: the rule specifies \"skip after 11 PM IST\" which is Nemesis's timezone. Since it's currently 7:11 AM IST, I'm well within the acceptable hours to send. There's no active group session visible, but that shouldn't prevent me from dropping a message to -1003606834639. The 10+ hour gap since the last group activity means it's time to reach out.\n\nI should also check whether I need to ping Nemesis - the condition requires 4+ hours elapsed since our last exchange, falling between 10 AM and 8 PM IST. Since it's 7:11 AM IST right now, that's too early to trigger the ping anyway.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6icrs8rkndg8_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"-1003606834639","message":"Saturday morning check-in 🖤 How's everyone doing?"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":177,"output":1186,"cacheRead":20416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21779,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775266905262,"responseId":"gen-1775266905-D10oWngv6CzgHQfcU57s"}}
