{"type":"message","id":"7a39419e","parentId":"54d70819","timestamp":"2026-04-04T01:42:07.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me summarize what I did:\n1. Checked the time - 1:41 AM UTC = 7:11 AM IST (morning for Nemesis)\n2. Checked pending tasks - none found\n3. Checked group vibes - last group message was April 3 at 15:21 UTC (~8:51 PM IST), more than 3 hours ago\n4. Checked group supervision - no sessions found to check messages, but based on GROUP.md no issues noted\n5. Checked Nemesis ping - It's 7:11 AM IST, before 10 AM, so no ping needed\n6. Group memory - no significant updates needed\n\nActions taken:\n- Sent a casual Saturday morning message to the group (Nrexya)\n- Updated heartbeat-state.json with the new group_message timestamp\n\nThis was a successful heartbeat with action taken. I should NOT send a summary to Nemesis since HEARTBEAT.md says \"Status: After tasks, send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken. Skip if nothing done.\"\n\nWait, I DID take action - I sent a group message. But the status says \"send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken\" - so I should send one?\n\nLet me re-read: \"- **Status:** After tasks, send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken. Skip if nothing done.\"\n\nI sent a group message, so action was taken. I should ping Nemesis a brief DM. Let me do that.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yiwu8lrmat57_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","buttons":[],"channel":"telegram","message":"Sent a casual morning check-in to the group 🖤 All quiet on the home front.","target":"7924461837"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":217,"output":708,"cacheRead":20800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21725,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775266921722,"responseId":"gen-1775266922-RMTGpsou7V8VV0KF