{"type":"message","id":"fcc9e98d","parentId":"8c12d0e7","timestamp":"2026-04-04T10:48:25.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check the current time and follow HEARTBEAT.md:\n\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 4th, 2026 — 10:48 AM (UTC)\nFor Nemesis (IST, UTC+5:30): 4:18 PM IST\n\nHEARTBEAT.md tasks:\n1. Time check first - Done: 10:48 AM UTC = 4:18 PM IST ✓\n2. Pending tasks - Need to check recent messages\n3. Group vibes - If 3+ hours since last group message, send casual msg. Skip after 11 PM IST.\n4. Group supervision - Read last 10 group messages. If Nexa said anything wrong, send correction.\n5. Ping Nemesis - If 10 AM–8 PM IST and 4+ hours since last DM\n6. Group memory - If significant group activity\n\nLet me check the last group message I sent - it was at 1:41 AM UTC (7:11 AM IST). That's about 9 hours ago in UTC, but in IST it's 4:18 PM now, so the last group message was around 7:11 AM IST - that's more than 3 hours ago (9+ hours actually).\n\nWait, let me recalculate: \n- Last group message: 2026-04-04T01:41:00Z = 07:11 IST\n- Current time: 10:48 UTC = 16:18 IST\n- So about 9 hours since last group message\n\nThat's more than 3 hours, but it's also after 11 PM IST now? No wait, 16:18 IST is 4:18 PM - that's afternoon, not late night. The \"skip after 11 PM IST\" means don't send after 11 PM at night, not after 11 AM. So it's fine to send.\n\nBut wait - let me check when I last pinged Nemesis. The last good morning was at 1:30 AM UTC (7:00 AM IST). Now it's 10:48 AM UTC (4:18 PM IST). \n\nI've pinged Nemesis about 9 hours ago, which is definitely more than 4 hours. Since it's between 10 AM and 8 PM IST, I should reach out to him. But first, I need to check the group messages to see if anything needs correcting before I initiate contact.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eaz9ei44dx18_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","buttons":[],"c