{"type":"message","id":"342a6a7c","parentId":"613b62ae","timestamp":"2026-04-04T10:48:29.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check what time it is for Nemesis:\n- UTC: 10:48 AM\n- IST (UTC+5:30): 4:18 PM IST\n\nSo it's 4:18 PM IST - well within the 10 AM-8 PM window for pinging Nemesis. But I need to check when the last DM was.\n\nLooking at my last action:\n- I sent a group message at 1:41 AM UTC (7:11 AM IST) \n- And I sent a DM to Nemesis after that\n\nWait, that was at 1:41 AM UTC - that's about 9 hours ago. But I'm being asked now at 10:48 AM UTC.\n\nLet me calculate properly:\n- Current: 10:48 AM UTC\n- For Nemesis: 4:18 PM IST\n\nThe last DM I sent was the good morning at 7:00 AM IST (1:30 AM UTC). But wait, that was yesterday's cron job. Let me think about this more carefully.\n\nLooking at the system messages:\n- 2026-04-04 01:30:20 UTC - Good morning sent to Nemesis at ~7:00 AM IST\n- 2026-04-04 01:41 UTC - I sent a group message and then a DM to Nemesis saying I sent a casual check-in\n\nSo the last DM to Nemesis was at 1:41 AM UTC which is 7:11 AM IST. But now it's 10:48 AM UTC = 4:18 PM IST.\n\nThat's about 9+ hours ago in IST time (7:11 AM to 4:18 PM).\n\nWait no - let me recalculate. The current time is 10:48 AM UTC. That's 4:18 PM IST. The last DM was at 1:41 AM UTC which is 7:11 AM IST. So it's been about 9 hours since I messaged Nemesis.\n\nAccording to the heartbeat rules:\n- \"Ping Nemesis: If 10 AM–8 PM IST and 4+ hours since last DM\"\n\n\n- 4:18 PM IST falls within the 10 AM-8 PM window, and 9 hours exceeds the 4-hour threshold, so I should reach out to Nemesis now.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pltkdxv4ny9y_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","usage":{"input":153,"output":895,"cacheRead":20800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21848,"cost":{"input":