It's 7:11 AM IST, before 10 AM, so no ping needed\n6. Group memory - no significant updates needed\n\nActions taken:\n- Sent a casual Saturday morning message to the group (Nrexya)\n- Updated heartbeat-state.json with the new group_message timestamp\n\nThis was a successful heartbeat with action taken. I should NOT send a summary to Nemesis since HEARTBEAT.md says \"Status: After tasks, send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken. Skip if nothing done.\"\n\nWait, I DID take action - I sent a group message. But the status says \"send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken\" - so I should send one?\n\nLet me re-read: \"- **Status:** After tasks, send Nemesis a brief DM ONLY if actions were taken. Skip if nothing done.\"\n\nI sent a group message, so action was taken. I should ping Nemesis a brief DM. Let me do that.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yiwu8lrmat57_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","buttons":[],"channel":"telegram","message":"Sent a casual morning check-in to the group 🖤 All quiet on the home front.","target":"7924461837"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"kilo-auto/free","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775266921722,"responseId":"gen-1775266922-RMTGpsou7V8VV0KFwI3S","__openclaw":{"id":"7a39419e","seq":22}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I sent a casual morning check-in to the group, updated the heartbeat state, and notified Nemesis. Let me check if there's anything else needed from HEARTBEAT.md:\n\n1. ✅ Time check - Done (1:41 AM UTC / 7:11 AM IST)\n2. ✅ Pending tasks - None from recent messages\n3. ✅ Group vibes - Sent casual message (last was 10+ hours ago)\n4. Group supervision - Need to read last 10 group messages (but no group session exists to read from)\n5. ✅ Ping Nemesis - Already sent good morning at 1:30 AM UTC (7:00 AM IST)\n6. ✅ Group memory - Not much happening\n\nI should check the last 10 group messages to see if Nexa said anything wrong. But